The missiles race towards Firestrike.  "You are no autobot," he 
yells as the missiles strike him.  LEaving him crimpled on the 
ground, his armour completely finished and his alloy metal scalded 
severely.  "Autobots would have stopped my fall, you don't hold 
leadership, you are as bad as I am.  Autobots, why do you follow 
such a coward as you classify us as.  Huh?" Thats what i thought 
he said as he used his one working arm to punch through a 
building.  A energon stream line poured out.  "BOOM" he saud as 
he raised his cannon and blasted.
